msgctxt "QL_Bottle_Mes_Desc"
msgid ""
"Follow the <1.se_co>letter <2.re_co>down the river without losing\n"
"sight of it, and find out who receives it. The\n"
"letter's casing is fragile, so take care when\n"
"pursuing it downstream.\n"
"\n"
"If you lose sight of the letter, return to Finley\n"
"to try again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "QL_Bottle_Mes_Finish"
msgid ""
"Sasan arrived safely at Zora's Domain and met\n"
"with Finley. Your part in the matter is concluded,\n"
"though it remains to be seen whether Sasan\n"
"can put on the muscle Finley hopes for."
msgstr ""

